": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 197451, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3702, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 506259, "username": "silypie", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/silypie", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e2f1dbb036de1978c1ddaffbd8435018?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e2f1dbb036de1978c1ddaffbd8435018?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e2f1dbb036de1978c1ddaffbd8435018?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1598965543, "last_modified": 1658109458}, "last_reply_by": "huangyx", "last_touched": 1677094409, "title": "以后台湾回归了，各位会考虑去台湾发展吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/918508", "created": 1677127759, "deleted": 0, "content": "“台湾回归”的实现应该只是时间问题，只是发生的具体时间可能是在接下来的十到二十年之间，或是在二十年以后。\r\n如果台湾回归，可以预料到将有许多政策支持，在这种情况下，大家是否会考虑前往台湾发展？", "content_rendered": "“台湾回归”的实现应该只是时间问题，只是发生的具体时间可能是在接下来的十到二十年之间，或是在二十年以后。<br />如果台湾回归，可以预料到将有许多政策支持，在这种情况下，大家是否会考虑前往台湾发展？", "last_modified": 1677127813, "replies": 149, "id": 918508}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1673261684", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1673261684", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 53415, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684", "stars": 8194, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 400182, "username": "weiwenhao", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/weiwenhao", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a342/616e/400182_mini.png?m=1674960065", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a342/616e/400182_normal.png?m=1674960065", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a342/616e/400182_large.png?m=1674960065", "created": 1554861515, "last_modified": 1674960065}, "last_reply_by": "weiwenhao", "last_touched": 1677122588, "title": "我觉得中国目前是解决不了养老问题的", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/918331", "created": 1677065028, "deleted": 0, "content": "忽然顿悟了，其实解决养老的问题很简单，包括之前的疫情问题也很简单，要看什么人去做。\r\n\r\n但是放在我国就基本是完不成的问题了，因为权利随着年龄的增加而增加，现在的决策者都是要退休的那一批。他们会不自觉的站在要退休的利益着想，也就是为自己的利益着想。 \r\n\r\nhttps://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/358755911  随便找了个资料，中国人大代表们的平均年龄是 53.77 岁。\r\n\r\n所以，让一批 50 多岁的人去出政策解决养老金不够的问题，解决年轻人以后没有养老金的问题，解决年轻人不愿意生孩子的问题，能解决么 (我也是担心自己交了这么多社保，以后毛线都没有)", "content_rendered": "忽然顿悟了，其实解决养老的问题很简单，包括之前的疫情问题也很简单，要看什么人去做。<br /><br />但是放在我国就基本是完不成的问题了，因为权利随着年龄的增加而增加，现在的决策者都是要退休的那一批。他们会不自觉的站在要退休的利益着想，也就是为自己的利益着想。 <br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/358755911\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/358755911</a>  随便找了个资料，中国人大代表们的平均年龄是 53.77 岁。<br /><br />所以，让一批 50 多岁的人去出政策解决养老金不够的问题，解决年轻人以后没有养老金的问题，解决年轻人不愿意生孩子的问题，能解决么 (我也是担心自己交了这么多社保，以后毛线都没有)", "last_modified": 1677065125, "replies": 132, "id": 918331}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1673261684", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1673261684", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 53415, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=16732